    fly "..."

    fly "..."

    fly "..."

    "(Ten minutes had passed and Bodhi had not called me. When I looked at his status, it said he was away. But 'away' where?)"

    "(Did his son enter his home office and make a mess of things? Did he go out to the grocery store to buy cereal? Was he busy beating his wife?)"

    "(Twenty minutes had passed, and I still did not get a call. He was most likely dead. This would be a problem, I should notify Drucker regarding his passing, we would need a new lead to replace him.)"

    "(At thirty minutes I suddenly got a call, the jingle that plays when someone makes a call felt similar to the teeth of jumper cables biting down on my johnston organ, but regardless, I accepted the call as quickly as I could.)"

    lead "Fly, I'm sorry but you have no future at this company."

    lead "I dislike working with you very very much, I do not even know how you even got this position."

    fly "..."

    lead "Once I have my own one-on-one with Drucker, I will tell him that I am unable to work with someone like you unfortunately."

    lead "Sounds good, ok so here is the documentation task I was talking about during standup. I want you to document the alerts that trigger in our application and what causes them to trigger I already created a table for you, here is the link:"

    "(When I clicked the link, there was no table there at all. What it looked like was plans to drive a truck with pressure cooker bombs into a local Chinese resturaunt.)"

    "(The conflict between the Indians and the Chinese have reached levels I could not have possibly imagined.)"

    "(This is also the only Chinese resturuant local to the area, although I have never slurped garbage, I did feel rather sad that I would probably never get the chance to slurp up some moldy General Tso's Chicken with eggroll.)"

    lead "Also, the business wants some edits to our current report generation script, they want to have separate reports based on the company name, I'll add more details on this in the ticket."

    fly "..."

    lead "Ok, sounds good, call me when you are done with the documentation task so I can review it. Thank you, have a good day."

    "(I decided to make a new blank page under the terror attack document and build the table with the alert details underneath it.)"

    "(Once I was done I notified Bodhi.)"

    lead "Hello, did you finish up figuring out what type of wood we were going to send to Mr. Zhangs house?"

    fly "..."

    lead "Not my problem, pull up the application logs I want to check something."

    "(As I was opening the console I accidentally clicked the wrong service, I quickly tried to go back to where I needed to but in my nervousness, misclicked the wrong service again.)"

    lead "Look, if you want to mess around, that is your choice, you obviously do not know what you are doing, randomly clicking around won't get us anywhere."

    "(I finally was able to pull up the application logs he asked for, but I was not sure what he was looking for.)"

    fly "..."

    lead "You can't explain anything can you? You have no idea what you are even looking at."

    fly "..."

    lead "Work with me here, explain what is happening."

    fly "..."

    lead "That's not what I am talking about at all, do you even know how to read?"

    fly "..."

    lead "Look, I know that things have been hard for you, I truly sympathize. But I do not think this position is a right fit for you. You need to have a serious discussion about this with Drucker."

    lead "I strongly suggest when you speak with him, you find a noose, and hang yourself right in front of him. Do not worry, I will provide the chair, there should not be any out of pocket costs for you."

    fly "..."

    lead "Sounds good, I'll connect with you once I finish the ticket on some new business requirements, thank you."

    "After the call was over, it was lunch time. I got up to get some sugar water and decided to listen in on the conversation my co developers were having."

