label Day_1_lunch:

    scene bg blackscreen

    co_dev_jai "Hey Thomson I wanted to ask, have you checked out the newest B48 film that has been released in theatres?"

    co_dev_thomson "What's B48?"

    co_dev_jai "They are a an independent entertainment company specializing in film and television, I can introduce you to some of the films they produce if you like."

    co_dev_thomson "Sounds awesomesauce bro."

    "There was a minute of silence before they both pulled out their phones and did not talk for about five minutes until Thomson started laughing."

    co_dev_thomson "Hahahahaha this is crazy bro, hey Jai look at this, it is a video of a monkey drowning its child in cement."

    co_dev_jai "Thomson this is rather concerning, is this real?"

    co_dev_thomson "Nah it's AI, I actually made it. I have an entire thing setup where I automate AI ideas to create videos and upload them to Youtube. I have made thousands of dollars off of this. It's crazy."

    co_dev_jai "That is certainly an interesting method of revenue generation."

    co_dev_thomson "I actually have a group chat where me and a bunch of people I know brainstorm different ideas, I'll invite you and you can help as well, It'll be another skill to add to your resume."

    co_dev_jai "Hmm, I will say it would be interesting to examine at the very least."

